reviewText: There's nothing like a Mister Rogers' Neighborhood story for the grandchildren!
Great video!  No previews which is nice.  Too pricey for 30 minutes.
I wish he was still being broadcast, instead of some of the innuendo-laden and violent  "cartoons" for children.  So informative and calming.
I enjoyed this DVD immensly. I have several others including some of the earlier episodes of Mister Rogers Neighborhood, I give it 10 Stars.
